data.text: @MLS If you're wondering why Beckham and @MLS are still bothering over a site they clearly don't want to be at, the vote on the site they want to be at is set for 11/6, and if they lose the vote, it's probably Overtown or bust. #MLS #DavidBeckham #MiamiMLS

Minor update: Bruce Matheson, the local resident who sued Beckham and @MLS over the Overtown site (and lost twice...hard), is filing a motion to reconsider his appeals court loss. Beckham/MLS response due in five days. #MiamiMLS #MLS #MiamiFreedomPark https://t.co/DB7UbYWDOw
This is of course subject to a motion to reconsider, and a potential appeal to the Florida Supreme Court. And, you know, Beckham wanting to build a stadium there. #MiamiMLS #MLS
